
This directory is the default location for static OpenIFS data files.

The data files can be downloaded from here:
https://sites.ecmwf.int/openifs/openifs-data/ifsdata/48r1/

Please extract the following tarballs into this directory:

 ifsdata_rtables_48r1.tgz
 ifsdata_climatology_48r1.tgz
 ifsdata_climate.v020_${RES}.tgz
   where ${RES} represents the horizontal grid resolutions you intend to use

Note: Depending on the number of extracted model grids, the data volume of
the downloaded packages can be large. By default you will be adding this data
in the $OIFS_HOME location. Please ensure that you have sufficient disk space
available. Otherwise you can replace this directory with a symbolic link to a
different location on your file system.

